biz.sudden.designCoordination.teamFormation.bottomUp.noticeboardAlgorithm
Class PartialOrder

java.lang.Object
  biz.sudden.designCoordination.teamFormation.bottomUp.noticeboardAlgorithm.PartialOrder

public class PartialOrder
extends java.lang.Object

A class to support the noticeboard algorithm - this holds the partial order between the states. This is never exposed to the process agents. It's very important to remember that the number assigned to a state is just an ID - currently it corresponds to the time at which it was added so might be mistaken for a linear ordering.

Author:
mcassmc

Add a new state to the partial order - with a specified list of states that it's bigger and less than. The function calculates the transitive closure of the set of previous/later states so there is no need to specify them in full.
